data.value:
This problem is probably due to the fact that the library files are locked by Windows. To resolve this issue, close the application, right-click on each of the files in the directory of the toolbox and click the "Unblock" button. Then rerun this application.
This is also not supported to run this application from a network share.
Or, there is no plugin file in the same directory where is this application.
